  "excerpt": "Remember the mug press I wrote about in this post ? Well it turns out you can use the same press for printing on water bottles! I was really excited about trying a simple black scripted quote/doodle on the aluminum…",
  "legacyPath": "/blog/2015/10/22/canteen-mugs",
